      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，所有路径最后都要汇聚到Exit Program。另外注意加密流程是连续的：Generate Key → Encrypt Plaintext → Decrypt with Key，这里Decrypt with Key也是最终退出前的状态。",
