      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来。HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault指向Validate Args，然后分五条线：-v/--version到Display Version Info，-h/--help到Display Help，-e flag到Generate Key，-d flag直接到Decrypt with Key，无效参数到Display Usage。",
